paragraph: Desiree Rollocks (born 4 September 1970), better known by her stage name Daisy Dee, is a Dutch singer, actress, TV host, stylist, and television producer. She is well known in German-speaking media. Daisy Dee hosted the German television show Clubrotation on Viva/MTV until 2003.
